    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute> <dateline><placeName ref="pl1017">Lichfield</placeName> June 3<hi rend="superscript">d</hi>. 1796.</dateline></opener>
                <p>I left <placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> on Saturday last, but neither hotpressed <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0034">Whiteford</title></bibl>
                    or letter had then arrived. my fears make me augur something amiss: but I trust that nothing materially amiss has befel 
                    <persName ref="pe0331">miss Bull</persName> or yourself. I am in a train of visit. shall stay two nights at a friend’s near 
                    <placeName ref="pl2576">Leatherhead</placeName>,<note type="editorial">  Pennant's friend near the town of Leatherhead, Surrey, has not been identified.</note>
                    and conclude at the primary object of our journey, a near relation of <persName ref="pe0238">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> Pennant</persName> 
                    at <placeName ref="pl2575">East malling</placeName> – on the 13<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. I shall make a short visit to <persName ref="pe0237">my Sister</persName>
                    in <placeName ref="pl0798">upper Grosvenour street</placeName>. a line sent there on the evening of that day will give me pleasure if it brings news of your welfare. 
                    I hope to contrive to find an hour to pass with you. my stay will not exceed four days &amp; those will be in full employ. every good wish attend <persName ref="pe0331">miss Bull</persName> &amp; yourself.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>Adieu
                    <lb/>Dear Sir
                    <lb/>Y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> most truely</salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <stamp type="postmark"><placeName ref="pl1017">LICHFIELD</placeName>; A<gap unit="letters" quantity="1" reason="illegible"/>U 4 <gap unit="letters" quantity="1" reason="illegible"/>6</stamp>
                </p>
                <p><address>
                    <addrLine><persName ref="pe0313">Richard Bull</persName> Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> | <placeName ref="pl0759">Stratton Street</placeName> | <placeName ref="pl2035">Piccadilly</placeName> | <placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName></addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
